::Prowl::

Prowl tightens his hands around Iron Raptor as she slides hers around him. 
His spark must have done its job, Iron Raptor's arms were proving that.

The coils from his stark retract and the spark itself retracts into his 
chest, the chestplate closing. He feels lightheaded as his systems deal with 
the depleted level of energy due to the repair.

Prowl leans sligtly away so that his optics could focus on Iron Raptor's 
face. His spark feels like bursting as he looks into her optics.

"Are you feeling better?" He asks, concern and love mixed into his voice. The 
fact that he had accidently hurt her while kissing her was fresh on Prowl's 
mind, and it annoyed him greatly. He slides his hand on her side, making sure 
it was repaired.
